column3: str
There's nothing left to build now! Surely they could spare a paltry few minutes to come and collect these blasted things...
Complete 100 stellar missions in Sinus Ardorum to become eligible to undertake an additional quest.
Good day to you, <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>! Will you come and speak with me when you have a moment?
The Cosmic Exploration Initiative has barely taken its first steps. To truly blossom, it needs both your talents and your time!
<Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>! I'm so glad to see you. Will you come and speak with me when you have a moment?
I worry that other crew members may be in need of help but are too hesitant to ask for it. Might you keep an ear out for me?
Councilor Y'adebh's inspection couldn't have gone better. If I find another task in need of a measured approach, I shall be sure to come to you.
Complete 50 stellar missions on Phaenna to become eligible to undertake an additional quest.
Ugh, it pains me to think of the tasks left unfinished back at the Hub... Is there <Emphasis>anyone</Emphasis> who might have a free moment?
To undertake a new quest from Mumukko, you will need to complete her quests in Sinus Ardorum.
How are you faring, <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>? I could always use your assistance whenever you have some time.
Well, if it isn't the shining star who personally attended Councilor Y'adebh! I should like to speak with you again once your preparations are complete.
Do keep an eye out for fellow contributors in need of assistance. I'm sure they'd be grateful to avail themselves of your talents!
Your tireless efforts continue to amaze me, <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>. The initiative owes you a great deal indeed!
A pleasure to see you, <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>! I do hope you can lend a hand when you have a spare moment.
Complete 50 stellar missions on Oizys to become eligible to undertake an additional quest.
I can't help but think of all the work still left to do on Phaenna... Surely someone out there can spare their precious time?
To undertake a new quest from Mumukko, you will need to complete her quests on Phaenna.
I trust you are well, <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>. If you have the time, I would be grateful of your aid.
Thank you for assisting with my little survey. I wonder what the results might reveal?
